# CODEOWNERS

# Ownership strategy
# - Current mode: single maintainer ownership.
# - Deadlock prevention: branch protection should run in solo mode
#   (required approvals = 0, code-owner review = false).
# - Second approver rollout: when a second write collaborator is added,
#   uncomment the "dual-approval templates" section and replace
#   @SECOND_APPROVER with the real GitHub handle, then turn required
#   approvals and code-owner review back on in branch protection.

# Docs and Senderr docs

/docs/ @bitquan
/docs/senderr_app/ @bitquan

